| Do’s                                       | Don’ts                                          |
| ------------------------------------------ | ----------------------------------------------- |
| Think before you post                      | Don’t overshare personal info                   |
| Curate a positive, useful feed             | Don’t compare your life to others’ posts        |
| Protect your privacy and accounts          | Don’t join or fuel online drama                 |
| Set clear time limits for scrolling        | Don’t post while very emotional or intoxicated  |
| Use social media to build real connections | Don’t ignore how social media affects your mood |
